data.description: This home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for various purposes. Downstairs, there are 2 living rooms, and the option to utilize one of the bedrooms and bathrooms as a mother-in-law suite, a roommate's space, an office, or even an indoor gym. The tile flooring is great for pet owners, while the expansive master bedroom includes abundant storage, a sizable walk-in closet, and a luxurious oversized jetted tub for relaxation. The open-concept kitchen features a tile back-splash, a gas range top, and DOUBLE ovens, creating an ideal setting for hosting gatherings. Additionally, the privacy-fenced backyard includes a back deck and a decently sized yard. With a great location near beaches, a golf course, schools, and the Norfolk Naval Base, this home is truly Move-In Ready!
